  "article_text": "What You Can Build | Star Atlas Build\nSkip to contentStar Atlas BuildSearchK\nAppearance\nMenuReturn to top\nWhat You Can Build ​\nTools, games, guides, merch, dashboards, it’s all happening here. The Star Atlas community has already launched dozens of impressive projects. From on-chain automation tools to merch stores, here’s just a glimpse of what people are building and what you can create too.\nGameplay Tools & Automation ​\nEVE Eye Map Tools\nATOM Automation Tool\nSLY Assistant (GitHub)\nSA Dispatcher\nDashboards & Data ​\nAephia Ships & Tools\nGlobal Overview (Flipside)\nDAC Stats – Steven Sabol\nStar Atlas Explorer – The Club\nRedSpatula Tools\nHeimdall Ship Markets\nStardust Economy\nGalactic Dash\nCoexist Data Hub\nItalia Dashboard\nNFT Market Data Sheet\nEscrow & Markets\nS&B Escrow Service\nS&B Market\nGuides & Help\nstaratlas.help\nstaratlasguide.com\nItalia Guides\nAephia Guides\nIntergalactic Herald Guides\nGaliaCrafters SA 101\nThe Hologram Guides\nVnonymus-Star Academia (ES)\nSAGE for Small Players – YouTube\nGames\nTufa Attack – Arcade Game\nValley Arcade – Discord\nGuild Resources\nDAC Explorer – Intergalactic Herald\nGuild List – Atlessio\nDeepProfits\nMerch, Art & Fun\nGalia Merchants\nStar Artisan Etsy Shop\nDark Core Roasters\nGalia Art Station – 3D Ships\nProfile Picture Generator\nStar Atlas TV Merch Shop\nNews & Blogs\nThe Hologram\nAephia Medium\nAephia News\nThe Bounty Bar (ES)\nSpace Frogies (FR)\nUI & Browser Extensions\nSAGE Dark Mode\nWant to See Your Project Listed?\nJoin us on Discord and contact our moderators",
